5 (2) Subject to subsection (3), class three property is taxed at 2.16% 1.85% of its productive
6 capacity value.
7 (3) The taxable value of land described in subsection (1)(c) is computed by multiplying the value of
8 the land by seven times the taxable percentage rate for agricultural land."
